column14: garment sewing or decoration sewing. With the exclusive Husqvarna Viking Sensor System
column21:
super easy buttonholes and over 100 stitches.

This has the exclusive Husqvarna Viking Sensor System that senses the thickness of the fabric and lowers the presser foot for you. When you are in needle down it will raise the foot to the pivot position by doing nothing but stopping in the needle down position.

This is super accurate because with just a tap of your foot the machine does half of a stitch. This makes accurate ¼" piecing and inset seaming effortless. Once you sew with the Husqvarna Viking sensor system you won't ever want to sew without it. But of course you are in total control and can have this machine set to however you wish.

Also this model has the longer extended bed to make sewing bulky items easier
column22:
such as when you are quilting a quilt.

Accessories included are:
24" X 18" acrylic extension table made for this machine made by DreamWorld Sew Steady
